{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16side_level_act16side_03_beg","storyGroup":"act16side","storySort":6,"storyDependence":"act16side_level_act16side_02_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GA-3","storyName":"混血儿","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在拉特兰的街道，塞茜莉亚对那个伪装的萨卡兹小贩说：“你的角和我爸爸的长得好像......你也是萨卡兹吗？”","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16side/level_act16side_03_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16side_03","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":4,"next":6,"characters":["奥伦","菲亚梅塔","艾泽尔","塞茜莉亚","薇尔丽芙","莫斯提马","教宗","帕蒂亚","里凯莱","费德里科","安静的小贩","愉快的小贩"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g8_laterano_dwelling","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#3$1","id":6},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"$ponder_loop","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"是菲亚梅塔啊......嗯？你好像有点狼狈？","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"与你无关。","id":12},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"别这么大火气，要不要坐下来喝杯茶？","id":14},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别打哈哈，你为什么会在这里？莫斯提马没有提过你会支援。","id":16},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"因为薇尔丽芙也没有给我正式下令嘛。","id":18},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"不过我个人可是很愿意帮忙的哦？","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"莫斯提马说，还有一拨人在追这个小女孩，而且已经和你打过照面了，对吧？","id":21},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......是这样没错。","id":23},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"我听公证所报告说艾泽尔切断定位讯号之后，就猜到你可能会被截了。如果被对方抓到时间差，这女孩不就搞丢了吗？","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"我是不知道为什么莫斯提马不来帮你的忙，但既然她动不了，我就顺手卖她个人情呗。","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"让你和莫斯提马欠人情的机会可不多。","id":28},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......几个不成气候的散兵游勇，还拦不住我。","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"“小心驶得万年船”啊，菲亚梅塔。你这样很容易在薇尔丽芙那里落下把柄的。","id":32},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"噢，我说的是一句炎国谚语，就是做事要小心谨慎的意思。","id":34},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别卖弄了，奥伦，你就是喜欢这样说话才惹人讨厌。","id":36},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"不说笑了。既然你来了，那我的人情也送到了，后面就交给你吧。","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"或者，你需要我护送一程吗，可爱的菲亚梅塔？","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"不用了，再见，奥伦。","id":42},{"type":"Dialog","id":43},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":44},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":45},{"type":"dialog","id":46},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":47},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":48},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"执行者艾泽尔，把这个女孩交给我。","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你最好不要拒绝。","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"您是叫做菲亚梅塔，是吗？菲亚梅塔女士，我有一个请求。","id":56},{"type":"dialog","id":57},{"type":"character","id":58},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunload","id":59},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"好了，说吧，你的请求。","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别乱动，我不保证我的手一定很稳。","id":63},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......我知道我之前违背里凯莱前辈命令、关掉终端的做法很可疑，但......","id":65},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"请相信，我并没有背叛拉特兰。","id":67},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我没有完全遵从公证所的命令，是因为不希望塞茜莉亚遭遇不测......而且，我答应了她一件事。","id":69},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"这和我有什么关系？","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......我的请求是，让我随同您，一起和塞茜莉亚前往大教堂。如果教皇厅需要了解这件事相关的信息，我在也比较方便，不是吗？","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"话说在前头，如果你指望的是，只要你跟着去，就能影响上面对这件事的处理结果——我建议你不要抱这种幻想。","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"更进一步......如果你想的是什么，要是教皇厅对这个女孩的安排不合你心意，你就把人劫走......","id":76},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"就更别做梦了。","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"不敢。大教堂有铳骑驻守，我很清楚。","id":80},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"而且，我毕竟是拉特兰的执行者。之前我有所担忧，是因为不了解塞茜莉亚究竟是什么情况，也不能确定追着塞茜莉亚的究竟有哪些人......","id":82},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"现在我已经明白了，我会服从您的安排。","id":84},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"可以。","id":86},{"type":"dialog","id":87},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","id":88},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":89},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#9$1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"嗯......你是叫塞茜莉亚是吗？还走得动吗？","id":91},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......艾泽尔哥哥......","id":93},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......塞茜莉亚，要是太累了，我背你吧......","id":95},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我来抱她吧，你太慢了。","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（小声）艾泽尔哥哥......","id":99},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......没事的，不会有事的，塞茜莉亚。","id":101},{"type":"Dialog","id":102},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":105},{"type":"Character","id":106},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving","screenadapt":"showall","id":107},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":108},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$sjoyasorrow_intro","key":"$sjoyasorrow_loop","volume":"0.4","id":109,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":111},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"执行者艾泽尔·帕斯托莱，今天上午前往司提望区瑟法斯街7-265号执行遗体身份验证、遗嘱确认和守护铳回收任务。","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"近午，艾泽尔出现于司提望区中心医院，送诊一名八岁萨科塔女童，后以非常规方式离开。","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"司提望区瑟法斯街7-265号户主费莉亚·拉珀尔塔，今天上午病逝于家中，遗体已收容至安魂教堂。","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"瑟法斯街7-265号户籍登记人口为一人，社区记录的居住人口也是一人。","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"调查瑟法斯街7-265号的近二十年的房屋维护记录，发现七年前曾增筑地下室，承包商留下的单据显示建筑用途是储物。","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"这里是费莉亚·拉珀尔塔的资料照片和艾泽尔送诊女童的监控影像。","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"女童的来历，想必诸位已有结论。","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"另外，根据艾泽尔午前发来的回报，费莉亚·拉珀尔塔未留遗嘱，未作遗嘱预登记，理由也相当明确了：她希望尽量避免与公证所往来。","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"合理推断，费莉亚·拉珀尔塔自知时日无多，必定会为自己的女儿准备后路。","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"目前无法确定艾泽尔是否就是费莉亚·拉珀尔塔的委托对象，但根据艾泽尔的背调结果，几率较小。","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"结合菲亚梅塔发回的信息，更有可能的受托对象应当是......","id":123},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"迷途者。","id":125},{"type":"dialog","id":126},{"type":"playsound","key":"$book_close","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":128},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"莫斯提马，这就是你留在大教堂的原因吗？","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$2","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"只是暂时。","id":132},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"别那么紧张，薇尔。吃泡芙吗？","id":134},{"type":"Dialog","id":135},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":136},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":138},{"type":"Character","id":139},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g10_laterano_roof","screenadapt":"showall","id":140},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":141},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":142},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"$plot_loop","volume":"0.4","id":143,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":145},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","id":146},{"type":"CharacterCutin","widgetID":"1","name":"avg_npc_357_1#6$1","style":"cutin","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"-300","width":"200","block":"true","id":147},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":148},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"唉，幸好选了比较温和的方法。","id":150},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"要是菲亚梅塔来的时候，正好看到我干掉公证所的人，那就糟糕了。","id":152},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"别找借口了。你不和那个执行者啰嗦那么多，塞茜莉亚现在已经在先导身边了。","id":154},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"那是个执行者，帕蒂亚，事情还没有到需要我出手的地步。","id":156},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"而且我看那个执行者关心的事情相当单纯，他不过是动了一点恻隐之心，不忍心看可爱的小女孩遭遇不幸而已。","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"知道他在意的是什么，说动他就只是时间问题，何必动用暴力。","id":159},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"要不是菲亚梅塔来得太早......","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"所以说，还是要怪你没有拦住菲亚梅塔哦，帕蒂亚。","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"......我......","id":165},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"开个玩笑。","id":167},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"不过，那个人也真是运气不好，明明很简单的事，现在变得这么复杂......每次快得手，就会出意外。","id":169},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"这就是伟大的拉特兰给我们的试炼吗？","id":171},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"你又有信仰了？","id":173},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"有信仰的人才不会这么说话呢。有信仰的人呢，会将苦难当成试炼，又把这些试炼当成是什么......命运的馈赠？","id":175},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"你和他身边，这样的人不少吧？","id":177},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"......总比你这种自私的萨科塔要强。","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"接下来......应该怎么办？塞茜莉亚去了大教堂，还出得来吗？我们难道有办法从大教堂把她带走？","id":180},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"别着急啊，帕蒂亚。要论不想让塞茜莉亚踏进大教堂，我应该比你更不想......","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"不过，我们的牌也还没出完吧？","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"帕蒂亚，去跟着菲亚梅塔吧，别太近。","id":185},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"那你呢？","id":187},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"我忙得很啊。刚知道，还有人在找我呢。太受欢迎也是挺烦恼的。","id":189},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"......别把麻烦事引到我们头上。","id":191},{"type":"dialog","id":192},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","id":193},{"type":"CharacterCutin","widgetID":"1","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":195},{"type":"Dialog","id":196},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":199},{"type":"Character","id":200},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g12_laterano_office","screenadapt":"showall","id":201},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":202},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$sjoyasorrow_intro","key":"$sjoyasorrow_loop","volume":"0.4","id":203,"musicid":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":205},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"......嗯，看来接下来的线索很清楚了，你打算怎么办？","id":207},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我直接去找他。","id":209},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#5$1","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"呃......虽然我对你的......武力，没什么怀疑。但对方可是资历很深的万国信使，要是闹出乌龙，就不好了吧？","id":211},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"他与这件事有关。","id":213},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"......因为有关，所以要查，是吗......有时候挺羡慕你的思考方式。","id":215},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"不过，要是他也不知情，怎么办？","id":217},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"查了才知道。","id":219},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"也是。不管怎么说，万国信使和这样的事有牵连，都值得一查。","id":221},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#9$1","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"不过真没想到，费莉亚一个深居简出的普通萨科塔，深查一下，竟然能扯出这么多线头。一个黑户小女孩儿，一个万国信使......","id":223},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#6$1","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"还有......萨卡兹。","id":225},{"type":"dialog","id":226},{"type":"character","id":227},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":228},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":229},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":230},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":231},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":232},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#4$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"嗯？这就走了吗？又是连个再见也不说？","id":234},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#9$1","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"好吧好吧......","id":236},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"既然你走了。","id":238},{"type":"dialog","id":239},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_devicebeep","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":241},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"奥伦，别怪我，我可拦不住费德里科。","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"给你报个信，就算仁至义尽啦。","id":245},{"type":"Dialog","id":246},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":249},{"type":"Character","id":250},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g9_laterano_street","screenadapt":"showall","id":251},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":252},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"$m_dia_street_loop","volume":"0.4","id":253,"musicid":4},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......她睡着了。","id":257},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"她太累了。","id":259},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你刚才说，你答应了她一件事，是什么？","id":261},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我答应她，要帮她找到她的母亲。","id":263},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"母亲？等等，我记得莫斯提马刚才给我传了信息，她的母亲不是......？","id":265},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯，是的。我亲眼见到了遗体，在安魂教堂的仪柩车上。","id":267},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"那你为什么会答应......？","id":269},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......刚遇到她的时候，我还不知道。","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"之后呢，你告诉她了吗？","id":273},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......我说了。但可能，她在这个年纪，还不太明白，“去世”，或者“死亡”，是怎么一回事......","id":275},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......你也不容易。","id":277},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#9$1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你......别愁眉苦脸了。我想，教宗阁下不会太过......苛待，这个女孩的。","id":279},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"她叫塞茜莉亚。","id":281},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"菲亚梅塔女士......","id":283},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"叫我菲亚梅塔就行。","id":285},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"菲亚梅塔小姐......塞茜莉亚去了大教堂之后，还能离开吗，我在想......","id":287},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......我不能向你保证。但在我看来，不论如何，她获得了光环，那她就是萨科塔。","id":289},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"既然对象是萨科塔，无论是教皇厅，还是公证所，都应该遵循戒律。至少我是这样认为的。","id":291},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":292},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"就算她没上户口。","id":293},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......呃，重点是这个吗？","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"说不定可以补办。","id":297},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":298},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......","id":299},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":300},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":301},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"但是，塞茜莉亚的光环......有问题。","id":303},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我确实不太了解，混血萨科塔这件事，能严重到什么程度......即使刚才的万国信使阁下也暗示说塞茜莉亚不会有事。","id":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"但最近，外国使节们正齐聚拉特兰，对吧？","id":307},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"教宗阁下筹备了这么久的会议......在这种时间点，我很担心，塞茜莉亚是否会成为......有心人做文章的靶子。","id":309},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......你想得还挺多。","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"反过来，教皇厅为了避免这种可能性，又会怎么做呢？","id":313},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"菲亚梅塔小姐，我不知道我该不该想这些。","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"但我没法不去想。","id":316},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你别怪我说话直。","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"其实你想这么多，有什么用吗？这件事难道由你掌控？","id":320},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你既然知道塞茜莉亚有这样的危险，就该明白，现在对于塞茜莉亚，大教堂才是最安全的地方。","id":322},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":323},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......您说得对。","id":324},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":325},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......唔......","id":326},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"对不起，我睡着了......","id":328},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我们说话吵醒你了吗？","id":330},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"不，不是，我就是......","id":332},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"艾泽尔，是你的肚子在叫吗？","id":334},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":335},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......","id":336},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#4$1","id":337},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚，我帮你去买个甜甜圈吧。","id":338},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","id":339},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"甜、甜甜圈......好的！谢谢艾泽尔哥哥......","id":340},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":341},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"算了，我去吧，刚好把她放下来歇一会儿，手酸了。","id":342},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"（小声）你要留我和她待一块儿，我可应付不来。","id":344},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"不过，别想着轻举妄动，艾泽尔，我看得见你。","id":346},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#4$1","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......您还没相信我啊。","id":348},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":349},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"对了，把你的终端打开，不允许关机。","id":350},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":351},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"是，是。","id":352},{"type":"dialog","id":353},{"type":"character","id":354},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":355},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":356},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":357},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":358},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":359},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","id":360},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（小声）艾泽尔哥哥，这个姐姐之前对你好凶......我不敢说话。","id":361},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":362},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"她不是坏人，没关系的，塞茜莉亚。","id":363},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#4$1","id":364},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥......是不是不能带我去见妈妈了？只说声再见也不行吗？","id":365},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯......我们得先去一个地方，确保你的安全。","id":367},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"你妈妈的事情......我会和你解释。让我......想一想，可以吗，塞茜莉亚？","id":369},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......嗯。","id":371},{"type":"dialog","id":372},{"type":"character","id":373},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":374},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":375},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥，你听见了吗？","id":377},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":378},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"听见什么？","id":379},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue",